description:
It’s a place where you dream of being horribly murdered by Your Mother.

I thought it was a dream, but it also happened in reality. To survive, I decided to make a different choice from my dream.

The only way to survive is to meet the Empress, but the only one that I encountered was my half-brother, the Crown Prince, Rudan. When I thought I was wrong, he reached out to me…

“Can I stay here?”

“This is your room now.”

I just cried because I was hungry, but everyone was so kind to me.>
